# Claude Code Instructions for Iron Foundry

## Development Workflow
- ALWAYS commit after completing each TODO task
- Use atomic commits for each logical feature completion
- Test changes before committing
- Follow the commit message format: `feat/fix/docs: description`

## Quality Gates
- Ensure accessibility compliance (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- Test responsive design across breakpoints
- Validate industrial design aesthetic consistency
- Check reduced motion support

